To launch Jajuk : 
$ ./jajuk

To install Jajuk into your PATH and install the menu icon :
$ sudo ./installer

Jajuk requires :
- A JRE 1.8+ like : java-13-openjdk-devel.x86_64
CAUTION : do not use a headless (server) Java release.

- Recommended : mplayer
Check http://www.mplayerhq.hu/design7/dload.html for a list of Linux packages 

Manual and help at https://jajuk.info